devdoc.details: The smart contract for the created Campaign. It handles everything related to a specific Campaign that has been deployed

params._beneficiary: The wallet address of the beneficiary that is creating this Campaign
params._deadline: Timestamp of when the Campaign should be fully funded before it becomes inactive
params._fundingGoal: Funding Goal for the Campaign in cryptocurrency (SepoliaETH)

donate().details: Allows donors to donate to the Campaign

finalizeCampaign().details: Called when the Campaign's deadline has passed, and also handles the refund to all donors if the fundingGoal is not met by thenLikely needs to be called from the frontend

getCampaignDetails().details: Get all the Campaign details from its state variables

getDonors().details: Get all the donors of this CampaignLikely to be used by the frontend to notify just donors on events such as FundsWithdrawn and CampaignFinalized
